<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.1.7">
<l>vāṉuḷā ravarai valimaiyāl naliyum maṟikaṭa lilaṅkaiyār kōṉai</l>
<l>pāṉunēr carattāl paṉaṅkaṉi pōlap parumuṭi yutiravil vaḷaittōṉ</l>
<l>kāṉulā mayiliṉ kaṇaṅkaṇiṉ ṟāṭak kaṇamukil muracaniṉ ṟatira</l>
<l>tēṉulā varivaṇ ṭiṉṉicai muralun tirukkaṇṇaṅ kuṭiyuṇiṉ ṟāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who bent [his] bow with arrows equal to the sun</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the thick heads dropped like coconuts</l>
<l>From the king of those of Laṅkā of the swelling sea who,</l>
<l rend="indent">with [his] power, tormented those who dwelled in heaven,</l>
<l>Stands in Tirukkaṇṇaṅkuṭi, where bees</l>
<l rend="indent">which wander in nectar hum sweet tunes,</l>
<l>As thunder always rumbles in clusters of clouds, and clusters of peacocks</l>
<l rend="indent">which wander in the grove always dance.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
